
flowchart TD
  Start[Change Request Created] --> Review[Reviewed by PMs]
  Review --> Approved[Approved for Analysis]
  Approved -- No --> Close[Change Order Closed]
  Approved -- Yes --> Analyze[CR Analyzed & Estimated]
  Analyze --> Submit[Submit to PMs]
  Submit --> PMLimit[Within PM Approval Limit?]
  PMLimit -- No --> Steering[Sent to Steering Committee]
  Steering --> SteeringApproved[Approved?]
  SteeringApproved -- No --> Close
  SteeringApproved -- Yes --> Execute[CR Executed]
  PMLimit -- Yes --> Execute
